{"tid":123157,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨7名立法會議員提名曾俊華　胡志偉：（曾）最有可能「創造奇蹟」","createTime":"2017-02-16T15:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T17:22:57.000Z","uid":29009,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9d405f9cc1f997347771fefab703b74fd23183","tid":123157,"uid":29009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"手握30張選委票的民主黨，今晚召開會議，討論特首選舉提名取向，會後宣布該黨不會綑綁提名，但「推薦」黨員提名曾俊華參選，該黨7名立法會議員將提名曾俊華。至於身兼專業界別選委的其他黨員，民主黨容許他們跟隨所屬選委名單，提名曾俊華、胡國興或依公民提名結果提名。 <br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉會後稱，曾俊華能展示親和力，團結大多數港人，亦在聽取意見後，調整在人大8.31政改框架和《基本法》23條立法的立場，加上曾俊華最有可能挑戰特首選舉結果、「創造奇蹟」，故推薦黨員提名對方。他表示，最終投票策略須根據日後實際環境再作決定，該黨會再討論。<br />\n<br />\n會議約有30名中委或選委出席。民主黨黨團召集人涂謹申會後稱，坊間民調顯示，民主派的支持者大多支持曾俊華，若曾俊華不能入閘，民主派支持者以至香港市民均會感到失望，「不會放過我們」。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申相信，若曾俊華最終當選，這或代表中央調整治港政策，趨向寬容及和諧，「中央不是揀曾俊華做大壞事」，而在新形勢下，中央或提出新方案，取代8.31框架。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨未有透露身兼專業界別選委的其他黨員，有多少人會提名曾俊華。該黨立法會議員尹兆堅會後指，相信有部分人會提名胡國興。<br />\n<br />\nSee more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170216/s00001/1487254527101#sthash.rtUHRDA5.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170216%2Fs00001%2F1487254527101%23sthash.rtUHRDA5.dpuf&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=348bb02a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170216%2Fs00001%2F1487254527101%23sthash.rtUHRDA5.dpuf&h=1e8298aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170216/s00001/1487254527101#sthash.rtUHRDA5.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"20a308cef6ed3a28548dc11632211e2c711bfcb2","tid":123157,"uid":776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6a742c8fefdfaccec86c9bdc195c4defff48ee0","tid":123157,"uid":29009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:30:00.000Z","msg":"大家一齊跟我嗌<br />\n民主黨賣香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ab38ee25d281c316b09c61723656d2b5a04996","tid":123157,"uid":29009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:38:08.000Z","msg":"廿三條黎啦"},{"pid":"98c46c725aaad8e7ff8d4f1878a3ab8d1c5d43a9","tid":123157,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>創造廿三條奇蹟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527f721f1669b31b5390b87e96b319c0bc7491a2","tid":123157,"uid":81292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:36:39.000Z","msg":"民主黨真係冇撚用"},{"pid":"58821767228a7897bf6a7e8d3907bb3d650f2979","tid":123157,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"呢班人不斷重覆犯錯... 一個 &quot;you always agree with your boss&quot; 既人會創造乜Q奇蹟"}]}